    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Astoria</strong> is a 2D Isometric game about surviving and exploring an alien planet. You're an intergalactic cargo shipping pilot and something has caused your ship to crash on a strange planet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/ece3fdc659ffd2e0260bbd6b15daf43d.poster.avif?t=1770235554\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/ece3fdc659ffd2e0260bbd6b15daf43d.webm?t=1770235554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/ece3fdc659ffd2e0260bbd6b15daf43d.mp4?t=1770235554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE AN ALIEN WORLD</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources to aid with survival and contend with alien life forms, both hostile and friendly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/803a84ca86f9c49f49ca38c186dfd1cc.poster.avif?t=1770235554\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/803a84ca86f9c49f49ca38c186dfd1cc.webm?t=1770235554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/803a84ca86f9c49f49ca38c186dfd1cc.mp4?t=1770235554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SEARCH FOR LOST CARGO</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Locating any intact shipping containers and cargo is key to surviving on this alien planet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/0583f05b6a9f4d5f1ef32ba63b3b2eb4.poster.avif?t=1770235554\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/0583f05b6a9f4d5f1ef32ba63b3b2eb4.webm?t=1770235554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/0583f05b6a9f4d5f1ef32ba63b3b2eb4.mp4?t=1770235554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SOLVE PUZZLES AND DISCOVER ANCIENT MYSTERIES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover ancient mysteries and relics that might help along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/155e15e333a6857b2ac7eaff9be2642e.poster.avif?t=1770235554\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/155e15e333a6857b2ac7eaff9be2642e.webm?t=1770235554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/155e15e333a6857b2ac7eaff9be2642e.mp4?t=1770235554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FARM EARTH AND ALIEN CROPS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secure a reliable source of food by farming both alien crops and earth crops found from the cargo from the wreckage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/8d9007f5b841956ecbbc24ac12fff723.poster.avif?t=1770235554\" width=616 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/8d9007f5b841956ecbbc24ac12fff723.webm?t=1770235554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240620/extras/8d9007f5b841956ecbbc24ac12fff723.mp4?t=1770235554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUILD A CUSTOMIZABLE BASE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set up a base however and wherever you see fit! Set up and manage a power grid to power your habitat, greenhouses, lights and more!</p>",
